      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road! I've taken care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and show you around the car!",
