    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS, the engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates and Powerflex bushings to maintain geometric integrity under load. Drive is sent through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. While the exterior shows minor road rash typical of a spirited driver, the drivetrain and suspension syncopation remain tight and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
